    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                              <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287720/extras/6fb1c7e7163dd9926072619eeb4f3844.avif?t=1753509380\" width=108 height=120 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u> </u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287720/extras/cc8bde78d4b4433f42f88648d6a159a7.avif?t=1753509380\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287720/extras_big/cc8bde78d4b4433f42f88648d6a159a7.avif?t=1753509380 width=800 height=139 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>《ELISSA：卧室的缢吊尸》</i></strong>是一款黑白手绘风格的悬疑推理类互动叙事游戏。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >侦探小说家梅尔·基甸（MEL Gideon)在咖啡厅焦急地等待着那位神秘的写信人出现，然而接下</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >来发生的事情却让人未曾预料——在一间破败狭窄的房间里，出现了一具早已冰冷的尸体。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不同于她笔下那些繁复离奇的死亡场景，真正的死亡竟是如此简单.....</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287720/extras/17a21de648c68ed34ff7651400133314.avif?t=1753509380\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287720/extras_big/17a21de648c68ed34ff7651400133314.avif?t=1753509380 width=800 height=139 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287720/extras/ef329812a2d58b2055b5bef2d9937de6.avif?t=1753509380\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287720/extras_big/ef329812a2d58b2055b5bef2d9937de6.avif?t=1753509380 width=800 height=499 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>                                 ①指向点击：在探索过程中可以调查物品和物品细节</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287720/extras/4bbe7a7b7159c7f4f1b5c939ffaea594.avif?t=1753509380\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287720/extras_big/4bbe7a7b7159c7f4f1b5c939ffaea594.avif?t=1753509380 width=800 height=498 /></span>                                               <strong><i>②获取物品：方便随时查看物品和使用</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287720/extras/d3333d0b9c5cc92b8d19553b6150037d.avif?t=1753509380\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287720/extras_big/d3333d0b9c5cc92b8d19553b6150037d.avif?t=1753509380 width=800 height=499 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                      <strong><i>③信息记录：获得的人物信息、文字线索会自动记录在笔记本中</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287720/extras/45b208e024c59409618706bb0341c6c3.avif?t=1753509380\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287720/extras_big/45b208e024c59409618706bb0341c6c3.avif?t=1753509380 width=800 height=499 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>                                         ④破解迷题：通过破解迷题，获得隐藏线索</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287720/extras/b042b07735fbf98309e3ee71cfac1b15.avif?t=1753509380\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287720/extras_big/b042b07735fbf98309e3ee71cfac1b15.avif?t=1753509380 width=800 height=139 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287720/extras/8f247d4966659fbbf5a6ba0380aeca84.avif?t=1753509380\" width=800 height=560 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287720/extras/ce5a8f1e58d6d6fc74fb89d25eb19e52.avif?t=1753509380\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287720/extras_big/ce5a8f1e58d6d6fc74fb89d25eb19e52.avif?t=1753509380 width=800 height=139 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>操作简单：</i></strong>游戏操作简单易上手，但你仍需要通过收集线索、破解迷题、分析和思考来揭示真相。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>美术：</i></strong>以黑白手绘呈现独特的美术设计，为游戏世界营造出复古而阴郁诡谲的氛围。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>音乐：</i></strong>每首配乐都为角色与剧情发展独立创作，通过细腻的旋律与和声，呈现丰富而深刻的听觉体验。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                               <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287720/extras/6fb1c7e7163dd9926072619eeb4f3844.avif?t=1753509380\" width=108 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>                                   更多内容等待揭开，开启属于你的19世纪悬疑推理之旅。                                 </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>玩家交流qq群：482237438</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
